gst.ui.layout

Class MultiSplit.MultiSplitEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • gst.ui.layout.MultiSplit.MultiSplitEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    MultiSplit

    private class MultiSplit.MultiSplitEntry
extends java.awt.Container
    A pair of a Component and a Divider Button. Also stores its predecessing and successing pairs. If successor is null, then the Divider is invisible.
    Version:
    0.1.1 (07.06.2012)
    Author:
    Enrico Grunitz
